    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The gas and aerosol envelope that extends from the ocean, land, and ice-covered surface of a planet outward into space; used especially in reference to the earth where it is held by the force of gravity.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
